init involve dynamic access like Class.newInstance for custom user directives?\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented a dedicated `RuntimeInstanceTest` for `org.apache.velocity:velocity:1.5`.\n\nChanged:\n- Added `tests/src/org.apache.velocity/velocity/1.5/src/test/java/org_apache_velocity/velocity/RuntimeInstanceTest.java`\n\nCoverage intent:\n- `RuntimeInstance.init()` exercises default property loading:\n  - `setDefaultProperties(...)` resource access\n  - `initializeDirectives(...)` resource access\n- Invalid `userdirective` configuration exercises the legacy synthetic `RuntimeInstance.class$(...)` path via public configuration APIs.\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per workflow instructions.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ee6fa3f3f1b9914016a03270627ec81a39741cb55a0faf9ed\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1189, "output": 846, "cacheRead": 47104, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 49139, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778591481526, "responseId": "resp_0ee6fa3f3f1b9914016a0326fa38c481a381f36cadc9c55793"}}
